{
  "texts": [
    "In such cases, the few unique terms in the reports become critical in distinguishing between different diagnoses.",
    "Therefore, these two baseline comparisons provide reference points for measuring the overall performance of our models.",
    "Automatic evaluation of the reports generated by HistoGPT is a non-trivial task.",
    "Popular evaluation methods for natural language generation such as BLEU-4 60, ROUGE-L 61, and METEOR 62 primarily compare n-grams between two documents and may not effectively capture semantic similarities.",
    "In fact, two texts may describe the same phenomena in two different ways, making a word-by-word comparison unfair."
  ]
}